    • Method Detail

      • setValues

        public Tags.Builder setValues(Iterable<String> values)
        Sets a list of tags to apply to an instance. Tags are used to identify valid sources or targets for network firewalls. Each tag within the list must comply with RFC1035.
        See Also:
        RFC1035

      • add

        public Tags.Builder add(String tag)

        See Also:

      • setFingerprint

        public Tags.Builder setFingerprint(String fingerprint)
